Notes
-Feel free to explore different options: test to see whether it's better or not
-Create a citable version of your software with DOI (digital object identifier) code, make it available on Zenobo or Figshare
--Zenobo is used by the same group as the Particle Accelerator in Switzerland
-Build team culture through non-work activities
-Have a working product by Friday

-Overly detailed design document will distract from the core ideas
-Explain what the product does, and what the product DOESN'T do
-Check out the articles Heroux provided
